n = int(input())
    lst = list(map(int, input().split()))
    lst.sort()
    sum1 = sum2 = 0
    for i in range(n//2):
        sum1 += lst[i]
        sum2 += lst[n-i-1]
    if abs(sum1 - sum2) > 1:
        print("No Solution")
        return None

    ans1, ans2 = [], []

    for i in range(n//2):
        ans1.append(lst[i])

    for i in range(n//2, n):
        ans2.append(lst[i])

    print(*ans1)
    print(*ans2)

n = int(input())
    arr = list(map(int, input().split()))
    arr.sort()
    han = []
    chewie = []
    if n%2 == 0:
        for i in range(n//2):
            han.append(arr[i])
            chewie.append(arr[n-1-i])
    else:
        for i in range((n-1)//2):
            han.append(arr[i])
            chewie.append(arr[n-1-i])

        han.append(arr[n//2])

    print(*han)
    print(*chewie)
